Ambiente
To celebrate the release of his new album 'FOREVERANDEVERNOMORE', visionary musician and artist Brian Eno curates a selection of tracks from the album, his back catalogue and his wide-ranging musical influences. 

A Place We Once Walked -- Roger Eno, Scoring Berlin -- The Turning Year
Black Willow -- Loma -- Loma
Bright Red -- Laurie Anderson -- Bright Red
By This River -- alva noto, Ryuichi Sakamoto -- Summvs
Devi Prayer -- Craig Pruess & Ananda -- 108 Sacred Names of Mother Divine
First Light - Remastered 2004 -- Harold Budd, Brian Eno -- Ambient 2: The Plateaux Of Mirror (Remastered 2004)
Heruvimska Pesen -- Bulgaria Armsmusica Schoumen Chamber Music Collegium -- Le Mystere des Voix Bulgares
In a Landscape (1948) -- John Cage, Stephen Drury -- In a Landscape: Piano Music of John Cage
In a Silent Way -- Miles Davis -- In A Silent Way
Inclusion -- Brian Eno -- FOREVERANDEVERNOMORE
Last Night The Moon Came -- Jon Hassell -- Last Night The Moon Came Dropping Its Clothes In The Street
Loop Only: Wind On Water Reversed -- Robert Fripp, Brian Eno -- LIVE IN PARIS 28.05.1975
Meditation No. 2 -- Laraaji, Brian Eno -- Ambient 3: Day Of Radiance
Moss Garden - 2017 Remaster -- David Bowie -- "Heroes" (2017 Remaster)
Reflection (Excerpt) -- Brian Eno -- Reflection (Excerpt)
Slow Movement: Sand -- Roger Eno, Brian Eno -- Slow Movement: Sand
There Were Bells -- Brian Eno -- FOREVERANDEVERNOMORE
We Let It In -- Brian Eno -- FOREVERANDEVERNOMORE
Welcome -- Jon Hopkins, 7RAYS -- Music For Psychedelic Therapy
World Without Wind -- Brian Eno -- Music For Installations
